# Gallery privacy (eye control)

When the user asks for privacy or "hide" in the gallery: **do not decode or show thumbnails**—show neutral placeholders only. Do not implement blur-for-privacy unless they explicitly ask for blur.

The toolbar eye toggle maps to `PhotoStore.hidePhotosInGallery` and `setHidePhotosInGallery`.
